The paper deals with optimization of 5G wireless networks, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The use of big data and proactive caching involves handling and processing large amounts of data, which is a key aspect of data science (cs.DS) and database systems (cs.DB). The paper also addresses security concerns in wireless networks, which is a topic covered under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper involves the use of edge/cloud computing, which is a subfield of systems and control (cs.SY).
